data.description: This home sits in a cute, quiet neighborhood close to the mountains of Bountiful. This well-established community offers mountain views and mature trees. The fully-fenced yard includes a greenhouse, storage sheds, covered patio and an RV pad with a newly installed gate. Inside has so much potential with hardwood floors under the carpet. Purchase this home as it is and move in, or make it an investment and update it completely. Basement is stubbed for a bathroom. You can't beat the location! Schedule a time to come see this one in person!
